# Steps to run application

git clone https://github.com/vaaluvishnu5146/Node_Todo_BE.git

cd ManageTasks

npm install

npm start

# API
## 1.Heart beat
http://localhost:3000/

## 2. Get All Todos
http://localhost:3000/todos/

## 3. Create a Todos
http://localhost:3000/todos/createTodo

## 4. Update a Todos
http://localhost:3000/todos/updateTodo/:todoId

## 5. Delete a Todos
http://localhost:3000/todos/deleteTodo/:todoId

# Create .env file
Simple create .env file in root of project

## And add below data into .env:
NODE_ENV = production
HOSTNAME = localhost
PORT = 3000
